{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemechipcomponenttokensprovider\/colorcontentunselectedfocus"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/colorContentUnselectedFocus"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"colorContentUnselectedFocus","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticTokens","text":"MultipleColorSemanticTokens","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"colorContentUnselectedFocus","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleColorSemanticTokens","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticTokens"}],"extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","title":"colorContentUnselectedFocus","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeChipComponentTokensProviderC27colorContentUnselectedFocus18OUDSTokensSemantic013MultipleColormF0Cvp"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token colors.actionFocus","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of chip","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSFilterChip"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSuggestionChip"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllChipComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ChipComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Chip"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") ,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"), dimensions ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and border  (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemechipcomponenttokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","alt":null,"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider/colorContentUnselectedFocus":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"colorContentUnselectedFocus","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleColorSemanticTokens","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticTokens"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/colorContentUnselectedFocus","kind":"symbol","title":"colorContentUnselectedFocus","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemechipcomponenttokensprovider\/colorcontentunselectedfocus","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token colors.actionFocus"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"Theme Orange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}